      • Public Function SubmitBWTable(bwt As BoardwalkTable, Optional sComment As String = "") As Collection

        Public Function SubmitBWTable(bwt As BoardwalkTable, Optional sComment As String = "") As Collection
        Details:

        '---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        ' Procedure : SubmitBWTable
        ' Author : Nitin Dhaware
        ' Date : 4/23/2011
        ' Purpose : This function submits data within a boardwalk table along with the comments and returns transaction id of the submit action carried out on server.
        ' Note that the function automatically calls Presubmit and Postsubmit events associated with boardwalk table.
        ' These events must follow the naming convention as
        ' -Public Sub _Presubmit()
        ' -Public Sub _Postsubmit()
        ' where must be replaced by the actual boardwalk table name as viewed in "__BW_TABLE_PROPERTIES" sheet.
        ' Parameters:
        ' * Boardwalk table--That needs to be submitted.
        ' * Comments--Optional parameter concerning the submit that is being made for the corresponding transaction.
        ' Returns: Long
        ' * 0 (zero)--When there is no data to submit.
        ' * Transaction ID--That is returned by the server.
        '------------- --------------------------------------------------------------------------
